    SCARP MT EXONIC

    carbon (fire orange)
    12-G SRAM XX1 AXS

    • MORE TRAVEL. MORE PLEASURE.

      Never underestimate the impact of more travel on a race bike. Launched in 2020 the Scarp MT expanded the KTM MTB range. MT, short for marathons, combines the advantages of more travel with an ultra-light race frame.

       

      KTMs STRAIGHT-LINE-LINK technology matched with 115 mm rear and 120 mm front travel ensures optimum performance over long distances even on rough terrain. A trail-orientated specification ensures the pleasure of an extra-long marathon adventure. A 67.5 head angle, enough space for a second bottle cage, as well as a dropper seat post at some of the models, wraps up the MT concept. Available at five different price points and specification versions.

       

      With a weight of less than 10 kg, the top model SCARP MT EXONIC is absolutely suitable for cross country races. Like their big brother, PRIME and MASTER rely on a full carbon frame, while the entry-level models ELITE and PRO are equipped with an aluminum rear triangle.
